summary: This document contains property records related to various transactions involving the parcel located at 9 E 71st St, New York, NY. It includes details about deeds, agreements, and satisfaction of mortgages associated with different parties over the years.
keyFacts: The document lists multiple transactions related to the property at 9 E 71st St, New York, NY.
Transactions include deeds, agreements, and satisfaction of mortgages dating back to 1975.
Parties involved in the transactions include Birch Wathen School, St. Clare's Hospital, and Manufacturers Hanover Trust Company.
The most recent recorded transaction was a deed filed on 1/10/2012.
Several transactions were recorded in the 1980s, indicating a long history of ownership and financial agreements related to the property.
